{"id":14235,"date":"2025-09-03T15:49:13","date_gmt":"2025-09-03T15:49:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/?p=14235"},"modified":"2025-11-19T15:10:49","modified_gmt":"2025-11-19T15:10:49","slug":"salt-air-climate-care-hvac","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/salt-air-climate-care-hvac\/","title":{"rendered":"Salt\u00a0Air Climate Care"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>How It Started<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Salt-Air Climate Care had built a strong local reputation, but their online footprint didn\u2019t reflect the level of service they offered. The website was slow, their Instagram had no consistent strategy, and paid ads weren\u2019t even in play.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We stepped in to help them scale, digitally and locally.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-1024x640.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14236\" srcset=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing.webp 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Project Overview<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Salt-Air provides residential and commercial HVAC services across Palm Beach County. While they had loyal word-of-mouth traffic, they were missing out on leads from search, social, and paid traffic.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our goal: build a 24\/7 digital sales engine..<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"640\" src=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-11-1024x640.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14238\" srcset=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-11-1024x640.webp 1024w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-11-300x188.webp 300w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-11-768x480.webp 768w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/website-mockup-local-social-marketing-11.webp 1280w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>What We Did<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Phase 1: Website + Funnel Build<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Rebuilt the entire website with mobile-first Elementor design<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Installed our SmartForm\u2122 system to auto-collect name, service needs, phone, and email<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Set up email + SMS alerts for real-time quote follow-up<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Reorganized service pages for faster loading and better SEO<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Added click-to-call buttons across mobile view<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Result:<\/strong><br>\u2192 Site loads 2.7x faster<br>\u2192 Visitors stay 58% longer<br>\u2192 Form submissions doubled in 30 days<\/p>\n\n\n\n<center>\n  <blockquote class=\"instagram-media\" data-instgrm-permalink=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/p\/DJMY4oYKyBb\/\" data-instgrm-version=\"14\" style=\"max-width:400px; width:100%; margin:auto;\"><\/blockquote>\n  <script async src=\"\/\/www.instagram.com\/embed.js\"><\/script>\n<\/center>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Phase 2: Monthly Reels + Social Management<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Took over their Instagram account with a full content strategy<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Produced <strong>3\u20135 monthly Reels<\/strong> highlighting team, installs, repairs, and drone footage<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Boosted follower count from <strong>under 100 to 250+<\/strong> organically<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Increased engagement by <strong>425%<\/strong> in 60 days<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>View their Instagram: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.instagram.com\/saltairclimatecare\/?utm_source=chatgpt.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">@saltairclimatecare<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"450\" src=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research-1024x450.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-14237\" srcset=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research-1024x450.webp 1024w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research-300x132.webp 300w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research-768x338.webp 768w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research-1536x675.webp 1536w, https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/local-social-marketing-seo-research.webp 1720w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Phase 3: Google Ads Campaigns<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Built a local campaign targeting high-intent HVAC keywords<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Launched ads for \u201cAC installation,\u201d \u201cemergency repair,\u201d and \u201cHVAC financing\u201d<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Set budget caps and ROI tracking to avoid waste<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Created custom landing pages for each ad group<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Result:<\/strong><br>\u2192 36 qualified leads in the first month<br>\u2192 $19 cost-per-lead on average<br>\u2192 Booked jobs tracked to ad clicks<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Full System Delivered<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Mobile-optimized WordPress website<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>SmartForms with real-time alerts<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Branded visuals + local photography<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Monthly Reels shot and edited by our team<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>Fully managed Google Ads with tracked ROI<\/li>\n\n\n\n<li>SEO-ready blog template and homepage structure<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Salt-Air went from an outdated website and no marketing to a full digital machine running every day, bringing in leads, showcasing the team, and building brand recognition.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Want to Build a System Like This?<\/strong><\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>We can design your site, automate your lead capture, and drive qualified traffic, just like we did for Salt-Air.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><a href=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/book-call\">Book your free strategy call<\/a><br><a href=\"https:\/\/localsocialmarketingllc.com\/portfolio\">See more client examples<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Salt Air Climate Care came to us with a goal: modernize their online presence and grow. We built a bold new website, launched monthly video reels, and activated Google Ads to boost leads. Now they\u2019re ranking stronger, converting faster, and showing up with confidence.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":14190,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[123],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-14235","post","type-post","status-publish","fo